Description: type-based approach to internationalization; profiling libraries
 This package provides a library for the Haskell programming language,
 compiled for profiling.
 See http://www.haskell.org/ for more information on Haskell.
 .
 This package uses the same approach of type-safe URLs to create translated
 content. It has a simple syntax for translators, while allowing the full
 power of Haskell for applying complex grammar rules.
 .
 This package was spun off from yesod-core, and therefore the Yesod
 documentation is a good place to start in understanding this package.
 Please see http://www.yesodweb.com/book/i18n for more information.

